description:
Google Places, Maps, Roads, Search and Translate. 
Requests and Responses are complete with Google Api documentation.
releaseNotes:
V3.2.0
- Upgraded Newtonsoft.Json 10.x for netstandard1.1 package.
- Obsoleted and removed custom List implementation for query parameters.
- Improved http error handling (http staus vs. error response json). GoogleApiException always thrown on http request errors now.
- Search improvements:
  - Refactored requests and responses for Google search.
  - Added more request exceptions for illegal combinations of parameters.
  - Corrected all EnumMember attribute values, for Country enum values.
  - Fixed search response deserialization for CountryRestriction, FileTypes, Rights, InterfaceLanguage, DateRestrict, SiteSearch, and more.
- Added Pagination objects to search response (Query, NextPage, PreviousPage).
- Improved search test coverage.

V3.2.1
- Aligned places search request properties (Text, Radar, NearBy). 
- Fixed issue with missing properties on places search response.
- Fixed issue where filetypes wasn't correctly deserialized for web search response.

V3.2.2
- Enabled Gzip compression for search requests.
- Added support for multiple nested country restrictions anf logical operators for search requsets.
- Fixed issue with deserialization, when an http error occurred and no content was returned by Google. Proper exception is now thrown.
- Fixed issue where GeoLocation (gl) request parameter wasn't correctly passed in search requests.
- Fixed issue with TravelMode (mode) in directions request.
- Fixed lack of object disposing during response deserialization.
- Fixed deserialization of country restrictions (cr) in search responses (string).

V3.2.3
- Fixed issue with enum mapping for place location types and address components types.
- Improvements custom deserilazation overriddes.

V3.2.4
- Fixed issue with deserializing AddressComponent.Types. (Unmapped types will be deserialzied to Uknown)

V3.2.5
- Disabled Gzip compression (Google search)
- Fixed missing PlaceId in geocode request.

V3.2.6
- Added PlaceLocationType.SuperMarket.

V3.2.7
- Fixed issue with Avoid request property for Directions and DIstance Matrix.

V3.2.8
- Cosmetic improvements
- Improved Performance in Http serialization / deserialization.
- Added Gzip handler for Search api.

V3.2.9
- Added max 100 points validation for NearestRaod and SnapToRoad requests.

V3.2.10
- Fixed issue with wrong data on SpeedLimit response (int to double).

V3.2.11
- Added SearchPlaceType.Embassy enum type.

V3.2.12
- Added PlaceLocationType.Embassy enum type.

V3.2.13
- Fixed deserialization of location type enum values to fallback to 'unknwon' (when not recognized).

V3.2.14
- Fixed vehicle types naming for direction response deserilization.

V3.2.15
- Fixed issue when specifying multiple component types in maps geocoding and place auto-complete requests.

V3.2.16
- Fixed exception being thrown for places auto-complete when using 'regions' and 'cities' types in request.
- Added missing 'duration_with_traffic' property in elements of distance matrix response.

V3.2.17
-  Fixed wrong deserialization for places search types (some values was incorrect).
- Removed deprecated places search types.

V3.2.18
- Fixed problem with places search request not looking at EnumMemberAttribute.
- Removed Xamarin.Forms dependencies.

V3.2.19
- Fixed reamining issue with places search request type.

V3.2.20
- Fixed issue with min / max price level in querystring for places search request (text, radar and nearby).
summary: Google Places, Maps, Roads, Search and Translate API support (100%)
title: Google Places, Maps, Roads, Search and Translate.
